                     <interp inst="t18280410-75-person571" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to Mr. Daniels, a pawnbroker, of Mary-le-bone. I have a cotton handkerchief, which the prisoner pawned with an apron of her own, on the 9th of April; my duplicate was found on her.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
